dcterms:description: Flickr-Faces-HQ (FFHQ) consists of 70,000 high-quality images of human faces at 1024x1024 resolution, featuring a wide variety of age, ethnicity, background, and accessories. The images were crawled from Flickr and are aligned and cropped consistently.
dcterms:title: Flickr-Faces-HQ

dcterms:description: The Large-scale Scene Understanding (LSUN) dataset contains 10 scene categories, each with a considerable number of images ranging from around 120,000 to 3,000,000. The images are of size 256x256.
dcterms:title: LSUN

dcterms:description: SpaceNet is a dataset of satellite imagery containing around 67,000 square kilometers of very high-resolution imagery, over 11 million building footprints, and 20,000 kilometers of road labels. It features various areas of interest, including cities and regions like Rio de Janeiro, Vegas, Paris, and Shanghai.
dcterms:title: SpaceNet
